sendToOthers

void sendToOthers(boolean message)
Send a message to all out going ports except a port that it received latest. NOTE: This will work only for Bidirectional link. For Uni-directional link, it will work only if a label of incoming port is the same as out going port label. Otherwise, all out going ports will be sent.

Parameters:
message - A message that need to be sent

sendToOthers

void sendToOthers(java.lang.String msgLabel,
                  boolean message)
Send a message with a given message label to all out going ports except a port that it received latest. NOTE: This will work only for Bidirectional link. For Uni-directional link, it will work only if a label of incoming port is the same as out going port label. Otherwise, all out going ports will be sent.

Parameters:
msgLabel - A message label
message - A message that need to be sent
